metadata.name: Survivors #1
metadata.description:
In 2023, a highly contagious mutant virus monkey pox will occur, causing a global emergency. The confirmed cases become extremely aggressive within three days, lose intelligence, and attack humans to infect or devour them. All countries in the world declared a state of emergency, held summit meetings, and made various efforts, such as hastily developed a vaccine, but all of them were in vain. It was estimated, but it is impossible to even predict how many non-confirmed cases are because most of them are infected or preyed on by the attacks of the confirmed patients. Under these circumstances, the surviving people gathered in the US state of Michigan to build a city. It is the only safe city in the world because of its strong walls and army. Using unstoppable communications satellites, it is sending news to the world that Michigan has a safe city with high walls and an army.
Upon hearing the news, the survivors are still on an unwanted and dangerous journey to Michigan.
